'''''Ashkharatsuyts''''' (Աշխարհացոյց <small>([[Traditional Armenian orthography|traditional]])</small>; Աշխարհացույց <small>([[Reformed Armenian Orthography|reformed]])</small>), often translated as '''''Geography''''' in English sources, is an early [[Medieval Armenia]]n illustrated book by [[Anania Shirakatsi]]. It is about the geography of [[Armenia]], [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]], [[Iran]], [[Iraq]], etc. ''Ashkharatsuyts'' is the oldest book in [[Matenadaran]] on geography.<ref>[http://www.matenadaran.am/en/heritage/geography.html The Heritage: Geography]. [[Matenadaran]]. Accessed October 28, 2009.</ref>
