The '''Hatton Basin''' is a [[sedimentary basin]], located off the west coast of [[Ireland]]. It lies between the Hatton and Edoras Banks to the west and the Rockall Bank to the east. The age of the basin fill is uncertain, as its relationship to the [[Rockall Basin]].

