The '''Special Administrative Unit of the Network of National Natural Parks of Colombia''' ({{lang-es|Unidad Administrativa Especial del Sistema de Parques Nacionales Naturales de Colombia}}; '''PNN''')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parquesnacionales.gov.co/PNN/portel/libreria/pdf/PlandeManejoPNNCuevaLosGuacharos.pdf|title=Plan de Manejo Parque Nacional Natural Cueva Los Guacharos|trans-title=Management Plan: National Natural Park Cueva Los Guacharos|language=Spanish|publisher=National Natural Parks System|page=56|year=2005|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141225071942/http://www.parquesnacionales.gov.co/PNN/portel/libreria/pdf/PlandeManejoPNNCuevaLosGuacharos.pdf|archivedate=2014-12-25|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.unog.ch/80256EDD006B8954/(httpAssets)/17E6E8610CC98842C1257881004F7011/$file/Colombia+2010.pdf|title=Presentación de Información en Relación con el Artículo 7 |trans-title=Presentation of Information Regarding Article 7|publisher=United Nations Office at Geneva|date=April 30, 2011|language=Spanish}}</ref> is [[List of entities in the executive branch of Colombia|Colombian central agency]] that manages all the [[List of national parks of Colombia|national parks]] and [[National System of Protected Areas (Colombia)|protected areas]].

